### Careers in Motion

In a season of job drought or transition? Careers in Motion is a ministry that meets every Tuesday on the Dallas Campus to help job seekers navigate their transition with spiritual support, practical advice, and networking.

[ministry details](/ministries/careers-in-motion/dallas){: .btn .btn-info}

