### Watermark Resources Director of Marketing - Dallas Campus

We are excited to announce our search for the Watermark Resources Director of Marketing. Our desire as a ministry is to bring glory to God by equipping and inspiring churches around the world to be and make disciples. This key leadership role will lead a team of people through the development, oversight, and execution of all communication and marketing efforts for Watermark Resources. An ideal candidate includes a combination of high-strategic thinking, experience leading creative projects, attention to detail, and a heart to serve the “Big C Church". Must have 5+ years of professional experience in digital marketing and communications.

[apply](https://my.watermark.org/WatermarkForms/560?PositionId=107){: .btn .btn-primary} [full job description](//assets.ctfassets.net/hw5pse7y1ojx/4xRWdzK7dy4GdbkGzagNDm/7e9a9c90923b8650017d5c2a2652f11a/Watermark_Resources_Director_of_Marketing.pdf){: .btn .btn-info}

