### Kids Midweek Leader (Part-Time)

Watermark Kids is looking for fully devoted followers of Christ who are passionate to disciple and care for kids ages Preschool through Elementary. This position will care for kids by sharing God’s love through Bible stories, activities, crafts, songs, and play time while cultivating a culture of fun. No prior teaching experience is required. This includes paid and volunteer opportunities. For more details on this position, please see the complete [job description](https://assets.ctfassets.net/hw5pse7y1ojx/5t9lngTGhjR52Bypdx3fXj/10aea1725c83fa90dcf0b8ea407f1aad/Kids_Midweek_Part_Time_2022.pdf).

[Apply](https://my.watermark.org/forms/334){: .btn .btn-primary}

fields.body:
### Preschool Coordinator - Dallas Campus

Watermark Kids is looking for someone to join our preschool team to help us guide future generations to follow Jesus and be the church. We want a person who anticipates needs, takes initiative to solve problems, and does so while caring for the person right in front of them. You will recruit, train, and shepherd volunteers; you’ll write fun, engaging, and evangelistic curriculum; you’ll create spaces where kids are seen and welcomed, taught about Jesus, and safe and secure. Come be part of a great team. Must be a member or willing to pursue membership, and must have experience working with and/or caring for kids.

[apply](https://my.watermark.org/WatermarkForms/560?PositionId=103){: .btn .btn-primary} [full job description](//assets.ctfassets.net/hw5pse7y1ojx/5onBvAY7eM5NM389wjxbAw/bb2dcc7e57496fd39a7b1be93af52c1f/Preschool_Coordinator.pdf){: .btn .btn-info}

### Watermark Resources Digital Specialist - Dallas Campus

Watermark Resources is searching for a technologically proficient, detail-oriented, and servant-hearted candidate to fill the role of Digital Specialist. This position is responsible for implementing and managing all digital properties (including websites, social media, podcasts, email, marketing automation, etc.) related to Watermark Resources’ national ministries, conferences, and leadership content. If you enjoy implementing content, analyzing data, and identifying trends in a way that serves the “Big C Church", then this may be the role for you.

[apply](https://my.watermark.org/WatermarkForms/560?PositionId=109){: .btn .btn-primary} [full job description](//assets.ctfassets.net/hw5pse7y1ojx/7L41hZT6nGG3PHN2BsLfiU/7c4ea2de0f7b399f213a85a13596358d/Watermark_Resources_Digital_Specialist.pdf){: .btn .btn-info}

### Director of Operations - Rockwall Campus

We are looking for a Director of Operations to oversee the details and strategic leadership of our church plant. There is a lot to build as we launch a new church and we are looking for someone to develop systems, strengthen our organizational leadership, and take the vision and make it actionable. This person will both implement for the now and build for the future. Looking for a leader that is that is highly task oriented and strategic to compliment the vision. We are looking to take the Gospel into a community and make disciples, come help us do it!

[apply](https://my.watermark.org/WatermarkForms/560?PositionId=85){: .btn .btn-primary} [full job description](//assets.ctfassets.net/hw5pse7y1ojx/7HCPEOsmGd784Ga12MBiNK/5eb768f61ac7e937c8d571cd8954619b/Rockwall_Director_of_Operations.pdf){: .btn .btn-info}

### City Engagement Coordinator - Dallas Campus

At Watermark we believe God calls us to seek the welfare of our city and those who live in it. We are looking for a candidate who can model servant leadership and will be able to work alongside volunteer leaders and community non-profits to transform the community. Our ideal candidate will be adaptable, organized, and detail-oriented, responsible for executing strategic outreach initiatives as well as engaging our Body across different events. If you have a passion for community impact work, inviting people to use their time and talents, and experience in event planning, then this may be the role for you.

[apply](https://my.watermark.org/WatermarkForms/560?PositionId=122){: .btn .btn-primary} [full job description](//assets.ctfassets.net/hw5pse7y1ojx/2UksoHMMAXDFVS0fUXviz7/19dbcd9d0c02d666b91b56e71df6764a/City_Engagement_Coordinator.pdf){: .btn .btn-info}

### re|engage Assistant - Dallas Campus

The Watermark Marriage Team has the privilege of loving and leading couples from both inside and outside our church who want to grow in their marriage. We are looking to hire an administrative leader for the re|engage team who is responsible for communicating, executing, and helping plan our weekly ministry events. This position is key in helping move both participants and leaders through the small group process. If you are someone who loves people, organization, hospitality, and administration, we want you to apply!

[apply](https://my.watermark.org/WatermarkForms/560?PositionId=123){: .btn .btn-primary} [full job description](//assets.ctfassets.net/hw5pse7y1ojx/6itgHn83nUJdSg6UUyCJyV/f5069135ce841f29757cafde8ef46c46/reengage_Assistant.pdf){: .btn .btn-info}
